Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:12.93,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:21.92,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:35.06,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:39.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:44.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.98,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:53.54,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.00,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:20.53,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:29.41,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:12.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:21.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:35.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:39.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:44.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:53.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:20.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:29.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夢?還是我的幻覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,那是千真萬確的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,一切全都是從那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我用塔羅牌算起\N我的戀愛運的那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,100)}命運的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,100)}{\a6}崩壞之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見\N拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,幫我算一下命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,她到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,練習已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,下一批!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到,你嚴重遲到了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們這些選手練習遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨罵的可是我這個經理耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,抱歉,因為寫報告拖了點時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這些了,男生都已經測完了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的是最後一批!你的目標現在才要登場!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10…10秒64…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳\N好厲害,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長破了11秒耶!太厲害了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到女生了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,您準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信您一定可以成功除龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您兄長的失敗就由您…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了,巴爾卡斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會背對敵人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是再多躺一下子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幸好並沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑步的姿勢越來越漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為你從國中開始就很認真練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直沒辦法跑低於13秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能跑得像你一樣快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題應該在起跑的力道上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣奮力往前衝出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的墜子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這個啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我祖母的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很有趣喔 只要像這樣子擺動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就會像鐘擺一樣\N一秒一次地,一直擺動下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:08:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2,3,4,5,6
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7,8,9,10
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11,12,13
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14,15,16
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎\N17…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!我幫你把書包…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉!由加莉,我在叫你耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也說句話嘛,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕月堂的草莓麻糬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑠倉屋的起司蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湘南本鋪的銅鑼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意大利傳統店的薄荷冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上每天奉上不同的點心 我就放過你這次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是故意昏倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我突然目出來礙事\N你早就跟學長大有進展了,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打你喔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?\N咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有算過你跟學長的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…要是算出來的結果不好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要是喜歡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我不小心聽到學長他們的聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說學長…天野學長可能會去國外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能連縣大會都沒辦法參加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很明白你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是早點表白吧 不然會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不說一定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,小瞳 洗澡水放好了喔 小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩壞之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表遙遠相隔的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長要到國外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也見不到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的A?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很遺憾沒辦法跟大家一起參加縣大會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們一定會跑出好成績的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在那邊等你們的好消息!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長,到了那邊以後，請寫信給我們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請千萬別忘了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 學長 學長 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我有件事想請你答應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個墜子擺完13下前跑完100公尺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我低於13秒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你接受我的初吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別後悔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎,你準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣奮力往前衝出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7…8…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙是什麼人?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!\N小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男生…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…我在夢裏見到的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,同學…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,アブゲーン クァル ェ ジィアボ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄錯了!我們並不是魔界的住民!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要問你是誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法尼利亞的梵!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你聽得懂他說的話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩,你快逃吧!地龍要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想被龍吃掉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?這次又是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難過…我好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是你的對手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?你不是肚子餓了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吃我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棘手的獵物留到最後對付,是吧!那個女的,你快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!天野學長,往山邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你扭傷腳了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來背你\N學長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏應該就安全了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把劍根本就傷不了它的鱗片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人不會有事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男生會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險…上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小傷還用不著你來為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要謝禮是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就到我的城來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,你可別太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份謝禮只是為了表達\N將你們捲入這場戰鬥的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是因為有你的幫助\N讓我才能打倒那頭龍的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在神氣什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以為你會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為你會死掉…所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕耶!怕得不得了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會說聲謝謝嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道我就不該幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你被龍吃掉算了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球?!為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會看到地球?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裏靠近阿薩斯村
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?阿薩斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠相隔與「龍的A」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在終於明白其中的真正意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮與地球高掛在天空的奇妙世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:50.96,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是這顆星球的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:09.71,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:18.16,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:25.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:31.94,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:39.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.95,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.96,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:54.46,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:24:01.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,跟古書上寫的一模一樣,可以啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是艾斯嘉科尼?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:09.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:18.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:25.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:31.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:39.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:54.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:24:01.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

